title: Moment nine burglars emerge from a single car in West Virginia
description: CCTV footage has captured the moment nine people exited a single car before robbing a store in the US. The footage shows the silver Hyundia Sonata reverse into a parking spot outside a store north of Warrenton, Virginia, about 3.30am local time on October 15.   "The business is a vape and tobacco shop that also sells custom clothing and high-end and hand-painted tennis shoes," Fauquier County Sheriff's Office said. "These guys were in such a hurry they reportedly stole only the left shoes." The group is believed to also be behind a spate of other burglaries in the area. #cctv #robbery #WestVirginia #crime #burglarly

title: Train derailment disrupts Perth commuter network | 7NEWS
description: A train derailment at Bayswater Station has caused major disruptions to Perth's rail network, with an A-series carriage coming off the tracks near a critical junction. The incident has blocked the Midland, Airport, and Ellenbrook lines, forcing the cancellation of train services and deployment of replacement buses for stranded commuters. Work crews are attempting to lift the derailed carriage back onto the tracks using heavy equipment.
